extends layout 

block content
  .membership-container
    h1 Become a Sustainability Buddy 🌱

    p Join our community and unlock exclusive benefits as you contribute more!

    .tiers
      .tier.bronze
        h2 🥉 Bronze Member
        p Everyone starts here.
        ul
          li Automatically unlocked upon joining.
          li Access to recipe swaps.
          li View basic dashboard stats.

      .tier.silver
        h2 🥈 Silver Member
        p Unlock at 50 swaps OR 100 reviews!
        ul
          li Priority access to new recipe swaps.
          li Special silver flair on your profile.
          li Highlighted contributions in community feeds.

      .tier.gold
        h2 🥇 Gold Member
        p Unlock at 100 swaps OR 200 reviews!
        ul
          li Recognition on our featured contributors list.
          li Exclusive gold flair on your profile.
          li Early sneak-peeks at new categories or badges.

      .tier.diamond
        h2 💎 Diamond Member 
        span.badge(style="background: #bbb; color: #333; padding: 0.2rem 0.5rem; border-radius: 5px; margin-left: 0.5rem") Coming Soon
        p The ultimate status for elite contributors!
        ul
          li Personalized analytics.
          li Secret seasonal challenges.
          li 🎁 Surprise perks just for Diamond members.

    .progress-info
      h3 How to Level Up 🚀
      p Every 50 swaps or 100 reviews unlocks the next tier. Track your journey on your dashboard!

    .cta
      a.button(href="/dashboard") View My Progress →
